(e) Rules of Construction.--Nothing in this section may be       construed to--

(1) require a private entity to share information with the       Secretary;

(2) require a private entity to request assistance from the       Secretary;

(3) require a private entity to implement any measure or       recommendation suggested by the Secretary in response to a       request by the private entity; or

(4) require the adoption of the best practices described in       subsection (c).
